epealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/291/dA/tXIII/s1351/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–291, div. A, title XIII, § 1351(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/3606"},"text":"128 Stat. 3606","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Soviet Nuclear Threat Reduction Act of 1991, referred to in subsec. (c)(2), is title II of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/228"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–228","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1991-12-12"},"text":"Dec. 12, 1991","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/105/1693"},"text":"105 Stat. 1693","children":[],"tail":". The reference to subtitle B of the Act probably means part B of the Act because title II of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/228"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–228","children":[],"tail":" does not contain a subtitle B. Part B was set out in a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2551"},"text":"section 2551 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and was comprised of sections 211 and 212, which were repealed, respectively, by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/181/dA/tXIII/s1304/a/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–181, div. A, title XIII, § 1304(a)(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-01-28"},"text":"Jan. 28, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/412"},"text":"122 Stat. 412","children":[],"tail":", and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/291/dA/tXIII/s1351/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–291, div. A, title XIII, § 1351(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/3606"},"text":"128 Stat. 3606","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"id90a0c41d-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"delegationOfFunctions","id":"id90a0c41e-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Delegation of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For delegation of certain functions of the President under this section, see Memorandum of President of the United States, ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-04-21"},"text":"Apr. 21, 1994","children":[],"tail":", 59 F.R. 21619, set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s5854"},"text":"section 5854 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Authority of President under this section delegated to Secretary of Defense by section 2 of Memorandum of President of the United States, ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-12-30"},"text":"Dec. 30, 1992","children":[],"tail":", 58 F.R. 3193, set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s5852"},"text":"section 5852 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
